1. "Moje prijateljice* i ja smo se prošetale po gradu." (My friends and I went for a walk around the city.)

2. "Sve tri smo bile prijateljice* već od malih nogu." (All three of us have been friends since we were little.)

3. "Kao prijateljice* smo se zavele da ćemo zajedno učiti za ispit." (We promised each other as friends that we would study together for the test.)

4. "Moje prijateljice* se nisu nikada mnogo družile." (My friends never really socialized much.)

5. "Praznike smo proslavile sa drugim prijateljicama*." (We celebrated the holidays with other female friends.)